divs: sighting details[name removed\cms\tg] of oregon mufon suggested i report this. we were at the oregon gardens spending time with family. i love taking black and white pictures with my iphone camera using the hipstamatic app. there is a waiting stop for the shuttle at the top of the hill where the oregon garden resort is. on top of that stop there is a weather vane. at that time of day and the way the clouds were and the amount of light that there was i had a great shot, so i took it with my camera. a few days later after i posted the picture to facebook one of my friends made a comment about the strange object in the upper left hand corner of the picture. since i didn't know about the object at the time i took the picture i can't describe how long it was there or its actions.
Summary: Unknown object in black an white image
